                    <p class="text-n-600 text-sm leading-normal font-normal md:text-xl lg:text-2xl">
                      “Sending my daughter to SAI was the best decision we made.
                      The teachers are so supportive and genuinely care about
                      each child's success. The engaging curriculum sparked a
                      love for learning in her, and she's thriving academically
                      and socially. We're grateful for the positive impact SAI
                      has had on our child's life.”
                    </p>
                    {/* Name wrapper */}
                    <div>
                      <p class="text-2xl leading-normal font-semibold text-orange-500 md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
                        Mrs. Haokip
                      </p>
                      <p class="text-n-500 text-sm leading-normal font-normal md:text-lg lg:text-xl">
                        Policewomen
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buttons wrapper -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-20">
        <!--  Prev button -->
        <button
          type="button"
          id="prevButton"
          class="bg-n-100 border-n-200 hover:bg-n-200 flex size-11 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-full border p-1 md:size-14"
          data-prev
          aria-label="Previous"
        >
          <span class="inline-flex">
            <svg
              class="size-5 md:size-7"
